  {
    "title": "Hollywood Airport",
    "url": "https://maps.secondlife.com/secondlife/Santa%20Catalina/227/146/24/?title=Hollywood+Airport&img=https%3A%2F%2Flecs-destinations-secondlife-com.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimg%2F10223%2F50feebb0ed360174134765.jpg&msg=Hollywood+Airport+%28SLHA%29+is+a+popular+public+airport+in+Second+Life.+Located+strategically+on+the+edge+of+the+Blake+Sea%2C+the+airport+buzzes+with+activity.+It+is+a+wonderful+place+to+just+hang+out+and+watch+the+planes+come+and+go.+More+than+ten+commercial+airlines+operate+flights+out+of+SLHA.+Scores+of+flights+%28sometimes+more+than+100%29+using+all+manner+of+aircraft+take+place+to+and+from+SLHA+on+a+daily+basis.+Come+fly+to+the+airport+and+walk+next+door+or+take+the+monorail+to+enjoy+the+excitement+of+Hollywood+region.",
